# claude-multipane config — copy to ~/.claude/panes.conf and edit.
# One project per line:  <name> <worktree-root> <main-branch> <pane-count>
# Panes are the worktrees <worktree-root>_pane1 .. _paneN alongside the main worktree.
#
# Example (a project "xyz" with 4 panes, main branch "main"):
# xyz  /Users/you/Documents/xyz  main  4
